data.description: Don't miss this great opportunity to own this 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home on a quiet cul-de-sac. This home is near lots of amenities such as schools, parks, Wakonda golf course, restaurants, grocery stores and shopping. The main floor of this split level home features the one living space, dining room, and updated kitchen. Upstairs you will find the 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Leading to the basement area you will find another living room area with a wood burning fireplace, half bathroom, and laundry room. Downstairs has a finished living room area and a non-conforming bedroom with a storage room. The backyard has a newer deck, storage shed and inground pool perfect for entertaining. Schedule your showing today!
